chunks.cleaned_english_translation: Fifteen. Do not entice other clergy members. We strictly forbid anyone from enticing or accepting another's clergy member. The sacred canons impose severe punishment for this offense.
chunks.original_latin:
XV. Ne alienos item clericos sollicitent. Hoc quoque modis omnibus prohibemus, ut nullus
vestrum alterius clericum sollicitet aut recipiat,
quia gravis de hac re in sacris canonibus sententia
est.
